title: Live: Super Bowl 51, New England Patriots v Atlanta Falcons
text:
Super Bowl 51: New England Patriots v Atlanta Falcons live blog Updated February 06, 2017 10:01:53 Map: United States 
It's the climax of the NFL season, as the New England Patriots take on the Atlanta Falcons in Super Bowl 51 from Houston. Legendary quarterback Tom Brady is playing in a record seventh Super Bowl, and he and the Patriots are seeking to lift the Vince Lombardi Trophy for the fifth time. 
Follow every sack and touchdown in our live blog.
